  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Sequin Clan, 4th level <br />No matter the dance, you're always able to fit it into your style as you are a professional dancer of course. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Charisma by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>You gain expertise in Performance, and during a long rest, you may choose one jutsu that you know which has the word \"Dance\" within its name. When choosing this jutsu, it uses your Charisma modifier for casting if it doesn't already, and is affected by your Professional Dancer feature.</li><li>All Dance Performance jutsu and jutsus with the word \"Dance\" in their name have their chakra cost reduced by half of your Charisma modifier rounded up (min 1.) to a minimum of 1.</li></ul>",
